Assignment 4: Projections
Domenic Murtari (domenic.murtari@gmail.com)
Time taken to complete: ~2 hours

Offers both orthogonal and perspective projections. Scene
starts by being rendered in orthogonal view. 

Arrow keys used to rotate the scene
'+'/'-' to increase/decrease dim
PgUp/PgDwn to increase/decrease field of view
'm/M' to switch between projections
'a' to toggle axes
's' to toggle smoke animation
0 to reset view
Esc to exit
